{"tid":841614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國醫師赴日研修 看完AV胸襲日本OL被捕","createTime":"2018-09-29T15:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T03:50:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d28b4e5c6a3c72eb5b1877ff9ac511b95a94ef","tid":841614,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"一名赴日進修的中國籍男子因看完A片慾火難消，對1名日本女子襲胸猥褻，目前已遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，住在東京豐島區中國籍李姓男子，在上月14日因為喝了點酒又看了A片，在他走出門時看見1名30多歲的日本OL，心生淫念，伸出狼爪將她緊緊環抱，並且對他做出襲胸等猥褻行為，隨即遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，李男聲稱自己是中國醫生，為了進修才會來到日本。自從他5月來到豐島區，當地便發生了許多類似的猥褻事件。警方調閱監視器後研判，李男可能與這幾件案件都有關係，正進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2565884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2565884&d=%2FYj1B1gVb%2BCtfA9wV4Zofv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a535cb69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2565884&h=bcfab382\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2565884</a>"},{"pid":"72e210bd3e32c2cd44f30fd69830a0ac86d2b01d","tid":841614,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"又支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02cd9a175f577833e600462c15c3ef60cd869f7","tid":841614,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da75847d584c773aca42f107a8c5d7ace981e0db","tid":841614,"uid":50699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"稻中兵團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34525024136caa63082af16c252562c033adc727","tid":841614,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"並且對<span style=\"color: red;\">他</span>做出襲胸等猥褻行為<br /